Certainly! I’m Brennen Chadburn, a Machine Learning Engineer based in Spring, TX, with 7 years of experience in the field of Data Science. My expertise spans several areas including machine learning engineering, agentic AI, natural language processing, optimization, forecasting, and image classification. 

I hold a Master's degree in Artificial Intelligence from Northwestern University, which I completed in 2019. My professional focus has recently been on multimodal models and large-scale agentic systems. I’ve built applications for forecasting and image classification, processing thousands of quotes daily for a luxury e-commerce company. Currently, I’m involved in developing optimization and data science-based applications for daily pipeline operations at a Fortune 100 energy company.

If you have specific questions about my work, projects, or areas of expertise, feel free to ask!
